{
  "stem": "25423.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how to approach it because if you measure it by what we know today and by yardsticks of modern life, I think he perhaps was foolhardy because he resumed his position and his activities as a rabbi in the temple just as if nothing before.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the temple was packed every Friday and Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He continued to preach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And regardless of Stalin's terror and activities of the Russians in the city, he carried on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, in a variety of ways.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Personally, I was persecuted in the school because I was a son of a rabbi-- or as they used to say, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clergyman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the new management of the school, which came from the Ukraine-- among them also some Jews-- were haunting me because I was a counter-revolutionary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were many ways, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the atmosphere of paranoia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's well described.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was much more severe that-- what we know about conditions in the Soviet Union, which were described after the war until even Brezhnev's times.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was midst of Stalin's terror.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was terror.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 14 in '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father could be arrested any moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally could be arrested in the school for some counter-revolutionary activities, which was very strange.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And secondly, I was pointed out by this consort, which was organizer, which-- 'organizer of the Young Communists,' as an example of somebody who disrupts the school and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] causes sabotage.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, these were very dangerous things in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because by haunting me, she could provoke the arrest of my parents and deportation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't because of my social background.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
